    <item>
      <title>阿联酋迅速从监管机构的黑钱名单中删除</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/uae-removed-from-watchdog-s-dirty-money-list-in-fast-turnaround</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周五，阿拉伯联合酋长国被从全球监管机构的“灰名单”中除名，距离这个海湾国家被降级还不到两年，地方当局打击非法资金流动的努力也因此受到限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/uae-removed-from-watchdog-s-dirty-money-list-in-fast-turnaround</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔确认美国武器交换在俄罗斯抗议后停止</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/ecuador-confirms-us-weapons-swap-is-off-after-russian-protest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔总统丹尼尔·诺博亚在接受美国有线电视新闻网采访时表示，厄瓜多尔在得知俄罗斯数十年武器将运往乌克兰后，取消了与美国交换这些武器的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/ecuador-confirms-us-weapons-swap-is-off-after-russian-protest</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 15:25:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利寻求乌克兰和印度投资者拯救钢厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/italy-sounds-out-ukrainian-indian-investors-to-rescue-steel-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔治亚·梅洛尼 (Giorgia Meloni) 政府正在与国内、乌克兰和印度投资者进行初步谈判，商讨拯救意大利最大钢铁制造商的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/italy-sounds-out-ukrainian-indian-investors-to-rescue-steel-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 15:24:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前邮局老板保拉·文内尔斯 (Paula Vennells) 因参与地平线丑闻而被剥夺大英帝国司令勋章</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-23/former-post-office-boss-paula-vennells-forfeits-cbe-for-role-in-horizon-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前邮局老板保拉·文内尔斯 (Paula Vennells) 因在处理地平线危机后“使荣誉制度名誉扫地”而被剥夺了 CBE。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-23/former-post-office-boss-paula-vennells-forfeits-cbe-for-role-in-horizon-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 15:13:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国通过法律使个人使用大麻合法化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/german-lawmakers-approve-cannabis-bill-in-legalization-drive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国立法者批准了一项有争议的法案，将个人使用大麻合法化，为从 4 月 1 日起控制大麻消费铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/german-lawmakers-approve-cannabis-bill-in-legalization-drive</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 14:42:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国希望从冻结的俄罗斯资产中“释放经济价值”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/us-looking-to-unlock-economic-value-from-frozen-russian-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部一位高级官员表示，美国正在探索使用在乌克兰入侵爆发时冻结的 3000 亿美元俄罗斯国有资产的方案，以帮助支付这个饱受战争蹂躏的国家的重建费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/us-looking-to-unlock-economic-value-from-frozen-russian-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 14:35:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥夫拉多尔称他并不后悔分享《纽约时报》记者的电话号码</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/amlo-says-he-doesn-t-regret-sharing-nyt-reporter-s-number</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩兹·奥夫拉多尔为自己挑选一名《纽约时报》记者的决定进行了辩护，这名记者就美国对其盟友与贩毒团伙之间涉嫌关系进行初步调查的报告提出了问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/amlo-says-he-doesn-t-regret-sharing-nyt-reporter-s-number</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 14:34:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者押注危机即将结束，塞内加尔债券上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/senegal-bonds-rally-after-sall-vows-to-step-down-and-end-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔总统麦基·萨勒承诺在任期结束时下台，受到投资者的欢呼，此前他试图继续掌权，引发了数周的动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/senegal-bonds-rally-after-sall-vows-to-step-down-and-end-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 09:09:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒默访问乌克兰，俄罗斯在美国援助延迟的情况下取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/war-in-ukraine-more-russian-drone-attacks-schumer-arrives-from-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议院多数党领袖查克·舒默突然访问乌克兰，向总统泽伦斯基保证，即使在国会面临障碍，美国仍将落实下一轮援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/war-in-ukraine-more-russian-drone-attacks-schumer-arrives-from-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 08:19:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将豁免权之争带入他的机密文件案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/trump-seeks-dismissal-of-us-charges-over-handling-of-documents</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普要求法官驳回对他离开白宫后处理机密文件的刑事指控，理由是他受到总统豁免权的保护，这是他利用法律理论逃避起诉的最新尝试。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/trump-seeks-dismissal-of-us-charges-over-handling-of-documents</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 03:19:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
